data.description: 932 Rachel Anne Dr is a newly built single-family home located in Belmont, NC. Constructed in 2022, this property offers a spacious living area with three bedrooms and two bathrooms. The exterior of the home includes a large back patio with scenic views and ample space for outdoor activities and landscaping possibilities. With its contemporary design and modern features, this home presents a perfect opportunity for comfortable and stylish living. Close proximity to South Point High School, Middle School, grocery stores, and just 25 minutes to downtown Charlotte.
